text: Recall ut vos dictus O Moses nos non longer tolerate unus generis de food alias tuus Dominus produce nos such earthly crops beans cucumbers garlic lentils onions. He dictus vos wish substitute ut quae inferior ut qui est est bonus? Iit down Egypt vos invenit quod vos asked They incurred condemnation humiliation disgrace brought upon themselves wrath ex DEUS! Hoc because they rejected deus revelations killed prophets unjustly! Hoc they disobeyed transgressed
